1887	// Drives buc_native_path_capture directly: source buc_command.sh, force
1888	// BURD_OSTYPE, assert the normalized stdout (or, for the bare-absolute
1889	// unsurveyed shape, that the capture returns non-zero). The normalizer is
1890	// sentinel-free and reads only its argument plus BURD_OSTYPE, so this stays a
1891	// dependency-free unit test — no foundry kindle, no regime, no credentials —
